</title>
               <text>
                  <paragraph>Inactive ingredients: Aqua (Deionized Water), C13-14 Isoparaffin, Glyceryl Stearate, Helianthus Annuus (Sunflower) Seed Oil, Isopropyl Myristate, Laureth-7, M Polyacrylamide, Steric Acid.
</paragraph>
